# ⏰ Smart Alarm App

A Flutter-based Smart Alarm application with sleep reminder, snooze feature, background alarm ringing, vibration and localization support. Built using Bloc architecture and SharedPreferences for local state management.

---

## 🧩 Features

- 💤 Sleep Reminder with time picker
- 🔔 Background alarm ringing using `android_alarm_manager_plus`
- 📳 Ringtone playback via `just_audio`
- 🌐 Multi-language support: English, Russian, Uzbek
- 🧠 Bloc-based clean state management
- 🔧 Local storage using `SharedPreferences`
- 🛑 Ringing screen with stop button

---

